  "title": "MNE-somato-data-bids (anonymized)",
  "description": "This dataset contains somatosensory MEG recordings converted to BIDS format, including raw MEG data, anatomical MRI scans, and FreeSurfer-derived structural derivatives. The dataset includes forward models and boundary element models computed using MNE-BIDS for source localization studies. This is a standardized version of the MNE-somato-data originally distributed with the MNE-Python toolbox.",
  "methods_description": "MEG data were acquired and converted to BIDS format using MNE-BIDS. Anatomical T1-weighted MRI images were processed using FreeSurfer's recon-all pipeline with default parameters. Source space definition, boundary element models, and forward models were computed using MNE-Python functions (make_scalp_surfaces, watershed_bem). Head-MRI transformation parameters were derived from anatomical landmarks.",
